en_449625_0	Upon observation of a leakage along the Payankulam tank bund which provides water to Palampiddi area, troops of the 613 Brigade under the 61 Division immediately began repairs to avert a major disaster on Saturday (6) due to increasing water levels.
en_449625_1	32 military personnel of the 613 Brigade actively contributed to the repair on the bund by plastering and placing sand bags around the affected area.
en_449625_2	613 Brigade Commander, Colonel R.K.N.C Jayawardane supervised the repair work on the instructions of the General Officer Commanding, 61 Division.
